data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET. Buyer financing Fell Through. Introducing a superb new corner lot listing in Fort Lauderdale, this corner lot property offers the perfect blend of location and potential. Just a 15-minute drive from the beach and conveniently situated near major business centers, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts a spacious yard with ample room for a pool and outdoor living. Inside, the open floor plan allows for easy living and entertaining. Don't miss the chance to turn this property into your dream home.
